      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POCKET DIAL (9) was without a win before displayed pleasing improvement last start to score by 1.1 metres over 1740m at Riverina Paceway a week ago. Draws out a little on the second line and may need luck at some point. Leading hope in a similar assignment. KOOKY (5) lines up for the first time. By Downbytheseaside and hails from the Jackson Painting stable. Looks to have some ability based on a recent trial win and is sure to prove very hard to beat. NUGGETGOTAREASON (6) has been competitive of late and kept the ball rolling last time when 3.5 metres from the winner in fourth over 1740m at Riverina Paceway. Tackles a similar assignment and he can grab that well-deserved win. HIGHVIEW BONNIE (4) was out of the money on debut two runs ago then did a fine job to overcome a break and finish 3 metres from the winner in third over 1740m at Riverina Paceway a week ago. Won't find this any harder and she will be competitive again.",
